WEBVTT

22:56.830 --> 22:57.870 line:80%
what should we do?

22:58.070 --> 23:00.600 line:80%
I know I shouldn't
ask too much about the case,

23:00.680 --> 23:02.280 line:80%
but my sister is still young.

23:03.440 --> 23:04.720 line:80%
I was thinking

23:04.740 --> 23:07.140 line:80%
we could leave after the New Year
to lie low.
